{
  "stem": "21308.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I think it's fair to say that most people were preoccupied with their own problems.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think that is the best answer I can give you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody went around shouting, joy for Hitler, I can tell you that, any more than they did for Mussolini.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were always joking, saying the only thing Mussolini did, but he did it very well, he made the trains run on time in Italy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- but-- we-- nobody really wanted the Second World War, I'm sure that-- absolutely certain of it-- except Hitler.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I'm now talking with hindsight, as far as he is concerned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let's draw a line at '34 because my mode of life completely changed in '34.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Up till '34, you read the news with interest, but your prime task was to stay in employment, to help you play your part in the family.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, in 1934, I joined the regularly Army, as I've told you, with a view long-term of joining the police.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, once you joined the regular Army and got into the military machine, it was a little bit different.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The machine permitted you to make weekly payments to your mum and small children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then as far as the machine went for the family, my mother used to send me my local paper but that never had anything other than local news in it-- Fishing Club results, football results, hockey results, cricket results, agricultural shows, that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But inside the Army, there was already a feeling that things were not right.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
